'''卡波埃塔'''（Kapoeta）是[[南蘇丹|南蘇丹]]東南部的小鎮，由[[东赤道州|东赤道州]]負責管轄，位於首都[[朱巴|朱巴]]以東約275公里<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://distancecalculator.globefeed.com/Sudan_Distance_Result.asp?fromplace=Juba%20%28%29%20(Airport)%20&toplace=Kapoeta%20%28Sharq%20al%20Istiwa%27iyah%29&fromlat=4.872006&tolat=4.7716667&fromlng=31.601117&tolng=33.5902778 |title=Map Showing Kapoeta And Juba With Distance Marker |accessdate=2011-09-11 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303204645/http://distancecalculator.globefeed.com/Sudan_Distance_Result.asp?fromplace=Juba%20()%20(Airport)%20&toplace=Kapoeta%20(Sharq%20al%20Istiwa'iyah)&fromlat=4.872006&tolat=4.7716667&fromlng=31.601117&tolng=33.5902778 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，海拔高度677米<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.airportsearch.org/HSKP/Kapoeta-Airport.html |title=Elevation of 2,220 Feet Above Sea Level |accessdate=2011-09-11 |archive-date=2012-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120317130006/http://www.airportsearch.org/HSKP/Kapoeta-Airport.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，鎮上有機場設施，2008年8月人口約7,000。

